parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Drag Link Failure and Steering System Issues
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the drag link can cause the steering wheel to lose control, leading to accidents or loss of vehicle control.
symptoms: Loose or stripped threads on the drag link

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Steering System Recall Remedies and Welding Concerns
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The recall remedies, which involve welding the jam nuts to the adjuster sleeve, may not be a permanent or safe solution, potentially leading to future steering system failures.
symptoms: Concerns about the safety and effectiveness of the recall remedies
and difficulties with future alignments and repairs.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Premature Tire Wear and Alignment Issues
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Premature tire wear and alignment issues can lead to uneven tire wear, reduced tire life, and potentially cause accidents or loss of vehicle control.
symptoms: and difficulties with maintaining proper tire pressure.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of wheel studs can cause the wheel to separate from the vehicle, leading to loss of control, accidents, and potential injuries or fatalities.
Tire tread separation can cause loss of control, accidents, and potential injuries or fatalities.
Tire belt separation can cause loss of control, accidents, and potential injuries or fatalities.
Using a spare tire of a different size can cause loss of control, accidents, and potential injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: Spare tire is a different size
concern about safety while using the spare tire.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: TPMS failure can cause loss of control, accidents, and potential injuries or fatalities.
Hubcap failure can cause loss of control, accidents, and potential injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: Hubcaps come loose and fall off while driving.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Transmission failure can cause the vehicle to lose power, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle goes into limp mode
and stays in 4th gear; the transmission does not shift properly; the vehicle is unable to shift into gear.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Gear shifter failure can cause the vehicle to lose control, leading to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The gear shifter handle fractures; the gear shifter detaches while shifting out of park.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Excessive oil consumption can lead to engine damage and potentially cause accidents.
symptoms: The vehicle burns through a quart and a half of oil every 1000 miles; no leaks are visible under the vehicle or on the oil pan.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Rear axle failure can cause the vehicle to lose control, leading to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: 000 miles; the rear axle fails while towing a load.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Throttle delay can cause the vehicle to lose power, leading to accidents or near-misses.
symptoms: There is a delay in throttle response; the vehicle does not react immediately to accelerator pedal input; the delay is most noticeable when merging into traffic or passing other vehicles.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Unavailable parts for recall repairs can leave vehicles in an unsafe condition.
symptoms: Dealerships do not have parts available for recall repairs; the vehicle is left in an unsafe condition.
